          prompt = A gritty, candid street photograph captured on high-contrast 35mm film, focusing on the raw, unfiltered reality of urban life. The image freezes a spontaneous "decisive moment" with razor-sharp authenticity. Lighting is natural but harsh, utilizing deep, crushing shadows and intense highlights to create dramatic chiaroscuro. Textures are visceral and tactile—weathered concrete, peeling paint, and the grit of the street are rendered with hyper-realistic detail. The visual grain is prominent (resembling high ISO film), adding to the rough, documentary aesthetic. Colors are stripped back—either stark black and white or muted, desaturated tones that emphasize structure and emotion over vibrancy. The composition is immersive and street-level, prioritizing narrative tension and the chaotic beauty of the city.
